- cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) is another possible category as the paper deals with algebraic structures and finite axiomatizations, which are topics in discrete mathematics. 
- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is a possible category as the paper deals with semigroup operations, which are relevant to automata theory. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with algebraic structures and finite axiomatizations, which are relevant to programming language semantics.
